---
title: Crispy Chickpea Tacos with Roasted Bell Peppers and Guacamole
description: Tender-cooked chickpeas are great in everything from hummus to salad bowls. But sometimes, it’s nice to explore their crispy side by roasting them in the oven until they get nicely browned and toasty. They give just the right amount of crunchy contrast to these veggie tacos, which get filled out with bell pepper strips, guacamole, and a zesty lime crema.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b7dab0a30006c452d358326-d0b262a4.jpg
